  "texts": [
    "By means of rapid engineering, companies are improving the flow of consumer service contacts.",
    "When a customer says, \"I received the incorrect item,\" for example, \"May I return it?\"",
    "the system shouldn't have to negotiate a maze of support documents.",
    "A prompt may set the LLM to get the relevant policy, translate it into plain English & provide a direct action like beginning a refund or linking to a live agent.",
    "This not only saves customer time but also lessens the load on support staff."
  ],
